== Redmine People plugin changelog

Redmine People plugin - User management plugin for redmine
Copyright (C) 2011-2023 RedmineUP
http://www.redmineup.com/

== 2023-01-26 v1.6.3

* Added leave requests
* Added Hungarian translation (Krisztian Engi)
* Fixed attachments error
* Fixed textarea preview
* Fixed grouped order for people list

== 2022-04-11 v1.6.2

* Fixed disabled gravatar bug
* Fixed announcement description error
* Fixed empty next year events
* Redmine 5.0 compatibility

== 2021-05-20 v1.6.1

* Added Redmine 4.2 compatibility
* Fixed MSSQL birthday error
* Fixed vcard version for old rubies
* Fixed LDAP source error on People create
* Fixed avatar displaying bug for HTTP protocol
* Fixed reports permission bug
* Fixed people permission error
* Updated DE locale
* Updated BR locale

== 2020-11-10 v1.6.0

* Added department announcements
* Fixed work expirence date fields
* Fixed age announcement bug
* Fixed leave creation alert

== 2020-08-24 v1.5.2

* Added select2 for tags
* Dayoffs added to Calendar page
* Portugal locale updated
* Chinese locale updated
* Taiwanese locale updated
* Removed tags migrations
* Fixed group-by error
* Fixed last month bug for perfomance chart
* Fixed initial install error
* Updated vcard gem versions

== 2020-02-18 v1.5.1

* Costs and rates moved to Budgets plugin
* Added Italian locale (Marco Congia)
* Changed Chinese locale (Zelphar Yang)

== 2020-02-18 v1.5.0

* Organization chart
* Leave management
* Redmine 4.1 support
* Fixed issue csv export bug
* Fixed delete redirect bug


== 2019-05-22 v1.4.1

* User activity report
